org.lafayette.server.web

Class Registry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lafayette.server.web.Registry

  • public final class Registry
extends Object
    Registers shared core resources. Shared resources:
    • version
    • stage
    • database connection
    • depeendcy injector
    • servlet context parameters
    • data mappers
    • nonces
    All resources are initialized with default values so the registry never returns null.
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter
